This module provides functions to input and output JSON with STDIO to
let you plug together CrowPi sensors and displays using standard unix
pipes.

For instance, to send the distance sensor to the LCD:
sudo python distance.py  --json-stdio | sudo python lcd.py --json-stdio

To send the distance sensor to the segment display:
sudo python distance.py  --json-stdio | sudo python segment.py --json-stdio

To send the RFID sensor to the LCD:
sudo python RFID/Read.py --json-stdio|sudo python lcd.py --json-stdio

Status: At this stage, we've only plugged together a few sensors as an
experiment. If it's of interest, we'll add more.